title: Visit Your New Home, Steam Room, Pet Friendly
posting_body: ['VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Experience the tranquility of spacious, low-density garden-style apartment living along the banks of the wetlands in Redwood Shores!', 'Our community is being transformed into a modern, vibrant living center with an unparalleled quality of living.', ' Exercise in our large gym which is located adjacent to our indoor pool.', ' Enjoy the convenience and reliability of our package lockers for all of your deliveries, as well as the peace of mind that comes with living in a community so close to nature and yet not far from major employers, grocery stores and restaurants.', ' All of these features and many more are available to our residents.', 'Pets are also welcome here!', ' In order to assure the highest quality of living for our residents,
